Ni jabarani kibaru nunu, 1958 An Evening ni fred Astaire ɲɔgonfɛ, ye bonya kɔnɔtɔn sɔrɔ, a bɛ u la "Best Single Performance ni filimudilan"\n"Most Outstanding Single Program of the Year."
